# Test Cross Reference

> Include: ../catala/cross_reference.catala_en

Covers DefinitionConsistency (every severity level) and FeeConsistency.

## Shared definitions

```catala-metadata
declaration lpa_specific_rating content PermittedInvestmentDef equals
  PermittedInvestmentDef {
    -- includes_debt_instruments: true
    -- has_rating_requirement: true
    -- uses_specific_rating: true
    -- uses_generic_investment_grade: false
    -- maximum_leverage: 0.50
  }

declaration om_generic_grade content PermittedInvestmentDef equals
  PermittedInvestmentDef {
    -- includes_debt_instruments: true
    -- has_rating_requirement: true
    -- uses_specific_rating: false
    -- uses_generic_investment_grade: true
    -- maximum_leverage: 0.50
  }

declaration aifm_higher_leverage content PermittedInvestmentDef equals
  PermittedInvestmentDef {
    -- includes_debt_instruments: true
    -- has_rating_requirement: true
    -- uses_specific_rating: true
    -- uses_generic_investment_grade: false
    -- maximum_leverage: 0.75
  }

declaration standard_fees content FeeDefinition equals
  FeeDefinition {
    -- management_fee_rate: 0.02
    -- performance_fee_rate: 0.20
    -- performance_fee_hurdle: 0.08
  }
```

## DefinitionConsistency

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope Test_Consistent_SeverityNone:
  output status content DefinitionConsistency

scope Test_Consistent_SeverityNone:
  definition status equals output of DefinitionConsistency with
    { -- def_lpa: lpa_specific_rating
      -- def_om: lpa_specific_rating
      -- def_aifm: lpa_specific_rating }
  assertion status.rating_consistent
  assertion status.leverage_consistent
  assertion status.all_consistent
  assertion status.severity = None

#[test]
declaration scope Test_RatingMismatch_SeverityHigh:
  output status content DefinitionConsistency

scope Test_RatingMismatch_SeverityHigh:
  # The BBB-/"investment grade" divergence: LPA names a specific
  # rating, the OM uses the generic phrase. High severity.
  definition status equals output of DefinitionConsistency with
    { -- def_lpa: lpa_specific_rating
      -- def_om: om_generic_grade
      -- def_aifm: lpa_specific_rating }
  assertion not status.rating_consistent
  assertion not status.all_consistent
  assertion status.severity = High

#[test]
declaration scope Test_LeverageMismatch_SeverityMedium:
  output status content DefinitionConsistency

scope Test_LeverageMismatch_SeverityMedium:
  # Ratings agree; the AIFM agreement caps leverage differently.
  definition status equals output of DefinitionConsistency with
    { -- def_lpa: lpa_specific_rating
      -- def_om: lpa_specific_rating
      -- def_aifm: aifm_higher_leverage }
  assertion status.rating_consistent
  assertion not status.leverage_consistent
  assertion not status.all_consistent
  assertion status.severity = Medium
```

## FeeConsistency

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope Test_Fees_Consistent:
  output status content FeeConsistency

scope Test_Fees_Consistent:
  definition status equals output of FeeConsistency with
    { -- lpa_fees: standard_fees
      -- aifm_fees: standard_fees }
  assertion status.fees_consistent

#[test]
declaration scope Test_Fees_HurdleMismatch:
  output status content FeeConsistency

scope Test_Fees_HurdleMismatch:
  definition status equals output of FeeConsistency with
    { -- lpa_fees: standard_fees
      -- aifm_fees: FeeDefinition {
           -- management_fee_rate: 0.02
           -- performance_fee_rate: 0.20
           -- performance_fee_hurdle: 0.07
         } }
  assertion not status.fees_consistent
```
